column1: #: description: Event selection cutflow for SM background (pre-fit) and representative signal samples for the $1lb\bar{b}$ channel. The masses of next-lightest-neutralinos and LSPs are reported. Only statistical uncertainties are shown. The MC statistics for the signal samples is 28K
column3: respectively. Samples are produced with generator filters which selects $h \rightarrow b\bar{b}$ and $W \rightarrow l \nu$ decays. ``All events" for SUSY scenarios represent the total number of signal events for the models considered taking into account the BR of $W \rightarrow l \nu$ (0.324) and $h \rightarrow b\bar{b}$ (0.582).
